        <p>               
               nanti-pō
               <lb break="no" n="2"/>ttarayar<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>ku yā
               <lb break="no" n="3"/>ṇṭu Iraṇṭ-āvatu
            </p>
        <p>
               <lb n="4"/>Amaṉi-kaṅkaraiyar
               <lb n="5"/>makaṉ celva-vā
               <lb break="no" n="6"/>ṇa-rayaṉ vittū
               <lb break="no" n="7"/>r āṇṭu ceyvit
               <lb break="no" n="8"/>ta muka-maṇṭaka
               <lb break="no" n="9"/>m

            </p>
