      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1">
          <supplied reason="undefined">Fortune!</supplied>
        </p>
        <p n="1-3">Second year of Nantipōttaraiyar.</p>
        <p n="4-9">
               <supplied reason="subaudible">This is</supplied> the <foreign>mukhamaṇḍapa</foreign> that Celvavāṇarayaṉ, the son <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Amaṉikaṅkaraiyar had made <supplied reason="subaudible">when</supplied> ruling over Vittūr.
            </p>
      </div>
      <div type="commentary">
        <p n="1">On Nandivarman = Nandivarman III Pallava. See SII and IP.</p>
        <p n="5">On Celva-vāṇa-rayaṉ, son of Amaṉi-kaṅkaraiyar. See SII.</p>
        <p n="6">On Vittūr = Viccūr. See SII and IP.</p>
      </div>
